videos.description: Carsen Edwards comes off the high screen and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Boilermakers.
videos.headline: Purdue's Edwards drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Carsen Edwards gets another deep-ball to drop as the Boilermakers pour it on the Hawkeyes in the second half.
videos.headline: Purdue's Edwards putting on a show

videos.description: The Boilermakers perfect their offensive execution en route to a Nojel Eastern one-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Purdue runs offense to perfection
